file.name: specWithParametersAndRequestBodySchemas.yaml
file.content:
openapi: "3.0.0"
info:
  title: Spec with parameters and request body API
  version: 1
paths:
  /id/{param}:
    parameters:
      - schema:
          type: string
        name: param
        in: path
        required: true
    post:
      operationId: postId
      parameters:
        - schema:
            type: integer
          name: param
          in: query
          required: false
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/dataSetListInput'
      responses:
        '200':
          description: returns all input parameters in one object
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/dataSetListOutput'
components:
  schemas:
    forDefaultsTesting:
      type: object
      properties:
        optionalArrayWithDefaultItems:
          type: array
          items:
            type: integer
            default: 42
        requiredArrayWithDefaultItems:
            type: array
            items:
              type: integer
              default: 48
        apiKey:
          type: string
          format: password
          default: pa$$word
        apiVersionNumber:
          type: string
          default: 1
        apiUrl:
          type: string
          format: uriref
          default: http://localhost:8080/api
        apiCount:
          type: integer
          format: int64
          default: 123456789123456
        apiAvg:
          type: integer
          default: 1234567890
        isInternal:
          type: boolean
          default: true
        start:
          type: string
          format: date
          default: 2020-10-8
        someDateTime:
          type: string
          format: date-time
          default: 2020-10-8T00:55:00+03:00
        pi:
          type: number
          default: 3.14
        someUid:
          type: string
          format: uid
          default: 8282cbfd-f323-4b7d-bcc0-28f127c2b365
      required:
        - requiredArrayWithDefaultItems
    dataSetListInput:
      type: object
      properties:
        total:
          type: integer
        defaultsTest:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/forDefaultsTesting'
      required:
        - defaultsTest
    dataSetListOutput:
      type: object
      properties:
        pathParam:
          type: string
        queryParam:
          type: integer
        total:
          type: integer
        defaultsTest:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/forDefaultsTesting'
      required:
        - pathParam
        - defaultsTest
